trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfigurationCreated?displayProperty=fullName> event is raised when the first HTTP module in the web application references the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfigurationCreated?displayProperty=fullName>denne hendelsen oppstår når den første HTTP-modulen i webprogrammet refererer til den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfigurationCreated?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The first access of the this property causes a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object to be created and initialized from configuration.
trans-unit.target: Første tilgang for denne egenskapen årsaker en <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objektet er opprettet og initialisert fra konfigurasjon.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: You can access the newly created <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object through the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property in an event handler in order to examine or modify it.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til det nyopprettede <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objektet via <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen i en hendelsesbehandling for å undersøke eller endre det.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs"></xref> class with the specified federation configuration object.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs"> </xref> klassen med den angitte sammenslåingen konfigurasjonsobjektet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A> property to the federation configuration object specified by `config`.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A>federation konfigurasjonsobjektet angitt av egenskapen `config`.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration"></xref> object contains the configurable properties for the WS-Federation Authentication Module (<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule"></xref>) and the Session Authentication Module (<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule"></xref>) in a web application.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration"> </xref> objektet inneholder egenskapene konfigurerbare WS Federation godkjenning-modul (<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule"></xref>) og økten godkjenning Module (<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule"></xref>) i et webprogram.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the federation configuration object that was initialized from the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir federation konfigurasjonsobjektet som ble startet i konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object contains the configurable properties for the WS-Federation Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>) and the Session Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>) in a web application.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objektet inneholder egenskapene konfigurerbare WS Federation godkjenning-modul (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>) og økten godkjenning Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>) i et webprogram.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: To modify the configuration settings, you can set properties on the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object that is referenced by this property, or you can provide an new <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil endre konfigurasjonsinnstillingene, kan du angi egenskaper for det <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objektet som refereres til av denne egenskapen, eller du kan angi en ny <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objektet.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: The federation configuration object that was initialized from configuration.
trans-unit.target: Federation konfigurasjonsobjektet som ble startet fra konfigurasjonen.
